This mod allows increasing the cargo size of transports, mining ships, auxiliaries and carriers (including DLCs).

There are several cargo size variants to choose from:

[list]
[*]Cargo size x2
[*]Cargo size x4
[*]Cargo size x6
[*]Cargo size x8
[*]Cargo size x10
[/list]
All ship sizes (S / M / L / XL) will be adjusted for both NPC and player ships. Existing and new ships will receive the adjusted values.

[b]NOTE:[/b] To compensate for the increased mass ships can carry with the increased cargo holds, the flight characteristics of the ships (acceleration, speed, turning) are also adjusted. This guarantees that even with a full cargo hold, the ships can still be flown normally.

