[color=#d9ead3][size=3][b]InstallingðŸ”¸[/b][/size][/color]

Can be installed anytime, does not affect savegame files. Installing with Vortex is recommended.

[b][color=#d9ead3][size=3]UninstallingðŸ”¸[/size][/color][/b]

The mod can be uninstalled at any time. Ships will retain their cargo even if it exceeds their cargo capacity after removing the mod, so no cargo is lost.

[b][color=#d9ead3][size=3]VRO compatibilityðŸ”¸[/size][/color][/b]

The mod has [b]not been tested with VRO[/b]. As I personally do not use VRO, I cannot guarantee that it will work. I am open to creating a patch for VRO if one is needed, and if you can provide information on the required changes.

[b][color=#d9ead3][size=3]Possible ConflictsðŸ”¸[/size][/color][/b]

As the mod changes the flight characteristics of ships, it will conflict with mods that also change them. As other mods are unlikely to compensate for the cargo mass increase, I have set my mod to high priority. This should ensure that my mod's flight characteristics are used. If not, you will possibly experience some ships that are too slow or have poor acceleration.

